WEBVTT

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:13.919
It's all set now.

00:00:21.059 --> 00:00:23.920
Why are you looking at me?
What's there to look at?

00:00:25.460 --> 00:00:26.339
Nothing.

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:29.940
You're old and ugly,

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:33.179
with white hair and a bad temper.

00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:37.340
Zhu Helai, since I've been with you,

00:00:38.420 --> 00:00:40.060
you've been working on this case.

00:00:41.020 --> 00:00:43.219
I was the one who
cleaned out this room for you.

00:00:44.899 --> 00:00:46.560
But I get scared once I get in here.

00:00:46.780 --> 00:00:50.119
I'm scared that these figures
and suspects

00:00:50.119 --> 00:00:52.359
would come alive in my dreams
and chase me.

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:57.359
I'm scared if I accidentally touch
or move something, you'd yell at me.

00:00:58.579 --> 00:00:59.840
But what scares me more is...

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:04.780
One day you'd never
come out of this room.

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:10.640
Zhu, I'm not stopping you
from being a hero.

00:01:11.099 --> 00:01:14.640
But don't forget, you're my husband
and Qianqian's dad.

00:01:15.719 --> 00:01:17.079
I don't care what you do outside.

00:01:17.079 --> 00:01:19.859
I just hope you can come back
to us in one piece.

00:01:21.900 --> 00:01:22.799
This family

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:25.079
needs you.

00:02:12.300 --> 00:02:13.219
Zhang Wei.

00:02:13.580 --> 00:02:14.680
Come on in.

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:17.300
Zhu, come out. Zhang Wei is here!

00:03:25.914 --> 00:03:28.986
=The Silent Rift=

00:03:29.210 --> 00:03:31.962
=Episode 8=
(Surrender)

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:35.860
Here, Wei, eat something.

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:38.439
- Just leftovers.
- Mrs. Zhu, thank you.

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:39.819
You really care for me.

00:03:40.759 --> 00:03:42.539
Take your time. You two talk.

00:03:43.240 --> 00:03:43.860
Master.

00:03:51.460 --> 00:03:56.039
Alright, cut the act.
Tell me, why did you come here?

00:03:56.219 --> 00:03:59.219
Master, I'm not acting.
I'm genuinely hungry.

00:03:59.460 --> 00:04:02.360
You just cook potatoes and radishes
in the cafeteria every day.

00:04:02.500 --> 00:04:04.400
I need to eat some proper food, right?

00:04:04.860 --> 00:04:05.719
Get to the point.

00:04:06.620 --> 00:04:09.759
Master, in the police station,
I'm the team leader.

00:04:09.759 --> 00:04:13.120
But in here, I'm still your apprentice.

00:04:13.900 --> 00:04:16.540
If I did something wrong,
you should tell me.

00:04:17.300 --> 00:04:18.899
You did nothing wrong.

00:04:19.660 --> 00:04:23.519
I'm perfectly content just being
in the task force with you.

00:04:24.540 --> 00:04:26.819
Master, just scold me a bit then.

00:04:27.759 --> 00:04:32.040
Look at you, you seem
more and more like a leader.

00:04:32.339 --> 00:04:34.939
Look at the way you talk.
You sound just like Liu Hua.

00:04:36.139 --> 00:04:39.920
Chief Liu has been cultivating me
out of respect for you.

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:40.879
Cut it out.

00:04:41.660 --> 00:04:43.560
If you want to chatter, finish up

00:04:43.639 --> 00:04:44.660
and head back.

00:04:44.660 --> 00:04:46.759
No, Master, don't be angry.

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:52.420
Our case has hit
a dead end on all leads.

00:04:54.139 --> 00:04:56.639
I wanted to ask you

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:59.379
what kind of person
Meng Guangcai is in your eyes.

00:05:03.962 --> 00:05:06.600
(Beiyan Police Station)

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:09.540
What's going on?
Why release the Hao brothers?

00:05:10.100 --> 00:05:12.319
The victim suddenly
recanted his testimony

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:15.319
and said he accidentally
sawed his own hand while working.

00:05:15.819 --> 00:05:18.540
Nonsense! Lying
on the testimony is illegal.

00:05:18.660 --> 00:05:19.160
Yes.

00:05:21.819 --> 00:05:24.100
(Guan Gong statue)
That He guy was a wise fool,

00:05:24.379 --> 00:05:25.939
but you're simply a fool.

00:05:26.439 --> 00:05:30.040
Meng Guangcai, we've
known each other for so long.

00:05:30.259 --> 00:05:33.379
We didn't build affection alright,
but why built hatred?

00:05:36.259 --> 00:05:41.040
Back at the construction site,
people said you were quite loyal.

00:05:41.259 --> 00:05:43.040
That you're a principled man.

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:44.379
But how could a principled man

00:05:44.379 --> 00:05:45.759
- do such a thing?
- Guangcai.

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:46.819
Guangcai!

00:05:47.100 --> 00:05:47.660
Xue Qin!

00:05:47.660 --> 00:05:48.319
Let go!

00:05:49.819 --> 00:05:51.379
How did you find such a loser?

00:05:52.379 --> 00:05:54.100
Your man is too dishonest.

00:05:54.220 --> 00:05:55.600
We treated you so well.

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:57.600
Yet he colluded secretly to rebel.

00:05:57.879 --> 00:05:59.160
You got him wrong.

00:06:00.500 --> 00:06:01.879
In the entire market,

00:06:02.819 --> 00:06:04.319
Guangcai respects you the most.

00:06:05.759 --> 00:06:06.439
Really?

00:06:08.100 --> 00:06:10.040
What a hypocrite.

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:14.540
Playing loyal but trying
to betray us? Respect us?

00:06:15.540 --> 00:06:20.259
If Guangcai did something wrong,
I apologize on his behalf.

00:06:21.319 --> 00:06:22.879
But stop hitting him.

00:06:24.819 --> 00:06:26.259
I'll be honest with you.

00:06:26.540 --> 00:06:30.100
That police officer Zhu you know
has come here several times,

00:06:30.379 --> 00:06:33.319
kept asking us brothers about you.

00:06:35.160 --> 00:06:38.660
He asked how much money
you had when you first came here

00:06:39.220 --> 00:06:40.720
and how much you gave us.

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:43.259
We two have been covering for you.

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:47.439
We treated you so well,
yet you betrayed us?

00:06:48.819 --> 00:06:49.660
How to compensate us?

00:06:54.879 --> 00:06:56.379
We'll leave Baima Market.

00:06:57.500 --> 00:07:00.500
We'll leave the goods
and the shop. Okay?

00:07:00.500 --> 00:07:03.439
No! Think you can just leave?

00:07:04.540 --> 00:07:08.379
Your man is smart, lucky,
and knows how to make money.

00:07:08.819 --> 00:07:11.319
Of course, we have
to keep this golden goose.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:16.220
Look, our old rule
was we take 40 percent.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.160
Starting today,

00:07:19.379 --> 00:07:20.879
we two want 80 percent.

00:07:23.540 --> 00:07:25.100
Dad! Mom!

00:07:25.100 --> 00:07:27.040
- Xiaoliang!
- Dad!

00:07:27.100 --> 00:07:27.759
Guangcai!

00:07:28.259 --> 00:07:29.040
What are you doing?

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:29.720
Guangcai!

00:07:29.819 --> 00:07:30.819
Dad!

00:07:30.819 --> 00:07:31.879
- Behind me.
- Guangcai!

00:07:31.879 --> 00:07:33.220
Guangcai! What are you doing?

00:07:36.319 --> 00:07:37.100
Dad!

00:07:37.100 --> 00:07:37.759
Guangcai!

00:07:37.879 --> 00:07:38.720
- Dad!
- Guangcai!

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:40.040
- What are you doing?
- Meng Xiaoliang.

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:41.259
Dad!

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:46.879
Xiaoliang.

00:07:47.660 --> 00:07:52.000
You attend Class 3, Grade 2
at Beiyan Elementary School, right?

00:07:53.939 --> 00:07:55.160
I got it right, didn't I?

00:07:58.660 --> 00:07:59.259
Guangcai.

00:08:24.826 --> 00:08:29.160
(Beiyan County Hospital)

00:08:29.160 --> 00:08:33.100
Mr. Meng. Zhu Helai, Liu Hua's buddy,

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:35.659
suddenly asked about
that loan you took out.

00:08:35.659 --> 00:08:37.879
Anyway, all the paperwork
on my end is perfectly okay.

00:08:37.879 --> 00:08:40.759
As for what specifics
to share or not share...

00:08:41.500 --> 00:08:43.000
You need to handle that yourself.

00:08:44.039 --> 00:08:45.320
Okay. Thanks.

00:08:48.580 --> 00:08:50.039
Officer Zhu, I'm sorry.

00:08:50.039 --> 00:08:52.700
Officer Zhu, I committed a crime.

00:08:53.379 --> 00:08:54.779
It's all my fault.

00:08:55.139 --> 00:08:56.500
I shouldn't frame someone else.

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:58.399
I want to take the punishment.

00:09:12.226 --> 00:09:24.960
(Beiyan County Hospital)

00:09:25.779 --> 00:09:26.580
I get it.

00:09:27.899 --> 00:09:28.960
You got the injuries

00:09:29.779 --> 00:09:31.899
on your face by accident too, right?

00:09:34.039 --> 00:09:35.340
All thanks to you, Zhu.

00:09:35.639 --> 00:09:38.940
You talked big about
wanting to be a hero,

00:09:39.460 --> 00:09:40.720
but now you're just a coward?

00:09:41.178 --> 00:09:44.519
(Beiyan County Hospital)

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:45.580
Those two won't get away.

00:09:46.279 --> 00:09:47.659
Tell me if they act recklessly.

00:09:47.779 --> 00:09:48.720
Keep an eye on them.

00:09:59.580 --> 00:10:00.200
Zhu.

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:03.080
Be honest,

00:10:04.659 --> 00:10:05.960
haven't you suspected me?

00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:13.460
I don't know anything.

00:10:16.139 --> 00:10:17.279
Don't ask me anything.

00:10:30.080 --> 00:10:33.460
Your tolerance is off today.

00:11:07.899 --> 00:11:08.779
Fire!

00:11:08.779 --> 00:11:10.500
Fire! Put it out!

00:11:10.500 --> 00:11:11.840
Fire! Put it out!

00:11:11.840 --> 00:11:12.659
Fire! Hurry!

00:11:12.659 --> 00:11:14.460
Fire! Put it out!

00:11:14.539 --> 00:11:15.779
Put out the fire!

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:17.399
Fire!

00:11:18.139 --> 00:11:19.200
Put out the fire!

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:20.580
Hurry up!

00:11:20.899 --> 00:11:22.279
Fire! Fire!

00:11:22.279 --> 00:11:23.580
Put out the fire!

00:11:23.940 --> 00:11:25.000
Fire!

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:25.639
Hurry!

00:11:28.399 --> 00:11:29.152
Hurry!

00:11:29.500 --> 00:11:30.399
Hurry!

00:11:33.626 --> 00:11:36.544
(One month later)

00:11:37.580 --> 00:11:38.440
Here, Zhu.

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:41.080
Try my dishes.

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:48.580
Your tastes have changed.
Now you're drinking foreign liquor.

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:51.580
I didn't buy it. A client gave it.

00:11:51.580 --> 00:11:54.220
Lately, we've been
swamped at the market.

00:11:54.220 --> 00:11:55.960
It's been ages since we gathered, Zhu.

00:11:55.960 --> 00:11:56.779
- Have some.
- Okay.

00:11:57.220 --> 00:11:59.000
Everyone's busy, especially Guangcai.

00:11:59.580 --> 00:12:02.720
Since he took over Baima Market,
it's hard to get a chance to meet him.

00:12:04.580 --> 00:12:05.700
Without your help,

00:12:06.600 --> 00:12:07.648
I wouldn't come this far.

00:12:08.279 --> 00:12:09.340
Here, Zhu, a toast to you.

00:12:09.840 --> 00:12:10.340
Yes.

00:12:12.500 --> 00:12:13.639
Here, I'll join in.

00:12:20.080 --> 00:12:23.539
After you came back from Guangnan,
I really thought you were short on cash.

00:12:24.519 --> 00:12:27.899
Except the Hao brothers, your influence
is the biggest at Baima Market.

00:12:28.940 --> 00:12:30.580
Baima Market's position is important.

00:12:30.580 --> 00:12:32.539
Anything that happens there
is no small matter.

00:12:33.399 --> 00:12:34.399
The leadership

00:12:36.279 --> 00:12:37.399
takes the fire seriously

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:39.360
and asked about it many times.

00:12:40.340 --> 00:12:41.340
I want to know

00:12:42.779 --> 00:12:44.519
how much you know about that fire.

00:12:46.519 --> 00:12:47.340
Zhu.

00:12:47.639 --> 00:12:50.580
The firefighters were very clear
about that fire.

00:12:50.960 --> 00:12:53.440
They said it was caused
by aging electrical circuits.

00:12:53.960 --> 00:12:57.159
Baima Market's fire inspections
have always had safety hazards.

00:12:57.720 --> 00:13:01.340
However, there was definitely
the possibility that the fire

00:13:01.779 --> 00:13:03.960
was caused by sabotage.

00:13:04.840 --> 00:13:07.399
Guangcai, you were closest
to the Hao brothers.

00:13:08.200 --> 00:13:09.100
Who

00:13:10.080 --> 00:13:11.539
had grudges against them before?

00:13:15.340 --> 00:13:16.399
Let me put it this way.

00:13:17.960 --> 00:13:20.779
Every merchant had grudges against them.

00:13:21.659 --> 00:13:24.200
Zhu, Guangcai isn't
exaggerating one bit.

00:13:24.399 --> 00:13:27.080
Everyone knew about the Hao brothers
skimming and extorting

00:13:27.080 --> 00:13:29.399
in the market. You too, Zhu.

00:13:29.720 --> 00:13:30.519
I know.

00:13:31.340 --> 00:13:34.840
I also know that Guangcai
covered for those two brothers.

00:13:35.720 --> 00:13:36.580
I remember it all.

00:13:38.399 --> 00:13:41.080
Let me put it another way.
With the Hao brothers dead by accident,

00:13:42.700 --> 00:13:44.399
who benefits the most?

00:13:55.539 --> 00:13:59.700
Are you suspecting I'm related
to the Hao brothers' deaths?

00:14:00.159 --> 00:14:01.700
I never dared to think so.

00:14:03.039 --> 00:14:05.519
But you've involved in
every big or small incident

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:07.759
in Baima Market.

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:10.080
Why is it always a coincidence?

00:14:16.539 --> 00:14:18.159
What does it have to do with me?

00:14:18.500 --> 00:14:21.340
What benefit could I gain
from their deaths?

00:14:22.460 --> 00:14:23.000
Zhu.

00:14:24.159 --> 00:14:26.279
If you're here today to catch up,

00:14:27.399 --> 00:14:28.519
then we

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:31.720
can eat properly.

00:14:32.399 --> 00:14:36.639
But if you're here to pick a fight,
then there's no need to drink together.

00:14:37.779 --> 00:14:39.399
I came to see you today

00:14:41.200 --> 00:14:42.779
because I still see you as my buddy

00:14:43.779 --> 00:14:45.000
for our old times' sake.

00:14:46.279 --> 00:14:47.960
If one day I come with my colleagues

00:14:48.879 --> 00:14:50.039
in my uniform...

00:14:50.960 --> 00:14:51.460
Guang...

00:14:52.899 --> 00:14:54.340
If you really see me as your buddy,

00:14:55.460 --> 00:14:59.220
why hound me? With so many cases,
yet you keep targeting me?

00:15:02.159 --> 00:15:04.779
Robberies, fires,

00:15:05.200 --> 00:15:08.659
every crime must be
committed by me, right?

00:15:11.580 --> 00:15:13.279
Guangcai, what are you doing?

00:15:20.080 --> 00:15:23.039
Don't be fooled
by his presentable looking.

00:15:23.879 --> 00:15:25.759
His luck has been incredibly bad.

00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:30.539
Since childhood, life presented him
with nothing but obstacles,

00:15:31.019 --> 00:15:32.539
one after another.

00:15:33.759 --> 00:15:36.879
If it were an ordinary person,

00:15:37.879 --> 00:15:39.440
they'd be crushed for life.

00:15:40.379 --> 00:15:41.379
But he's different.

00:15:44.899 --> 00:15:46.279
Meng Guangcai,

00:15:47.960 --> 00:15:51.500
half gentleman, half villain,

00:15:52.500 --> 00:15:53.899
is full of complexity.

00:15:54.960 --> 00:15:58.460
It's this complexity
that makes him truly stand out.

00:15:59.220 --> 00:16:02.340
It draws a bunch of people
to follow him,

00:16:02.840 --> 00:16:04.399
work with him,

00:16:05.340 --> 00:16:07.720
even commit extreme acts.

00:16:09.960 --> 00:16:11.600
So if that's the case,

00:16:12.100 --> 00:16:13.340
Master, I understand

00:16:13.840 --> 00:16:17.279
why those people are so loyal
to Meng Guangcai.

00:16:17.720 --> 00:16:19.779
You knew him back in Shaguai Village.

00:16:20.460 --> 00:16:23.220
Besides Jiao Lijun and Wang Dazhu,
do you remember

00:16:23.639 --> 00:16:25.659
if Meng Guangcai has
any other old acquaintances?

00:16:31.220 --> 00:16:32.019
Yes.

00:16:32.899 --> 00:16:33.779
Who is it?

00:16:39.580 --> 00:16:41.000
Huang Mantang?

00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:45.899
Master, I've heard that name.

00:16:46.159 --> 00:16:47.220
Let's go find him.

00:16:47.899 --> 00:16:48.779
We can't.

00:16:49.659 --> 00:16:52.159
He's not at Caisheng Group now.

00:16:54.840 --> 00:16:55.899
In 1970,

00:16:56.600 --> 00:16:59.220
Huang Mantang was born
in Shaguai Village, Magou Town.

00:17:00.279 --> 00:17:03.399
His mother died when he was very young.

00:17:04.460 --> 00:17:06.599
And his father was a gambler,
drowning in debt.

00:17:08.019 --> 00:17:11.599
In 1988, his father ran away
to escape debt collectors.

00:17:12.460 --> 00:17:14.660
He then turned to Chen Rongfa.

00:17:15.720 --> 00:17:18.579
Zuo Long, failing to collect the debt,
robbed Chen Rongfa.

00:17:19.660 --> 00:17:22.819
This directly sparked conflict
between Meng Guangcai and Zuo Long.

00:17:23.559 --> 00:17:27.559
In 1991, Huang Mantang went to Beiyan
to join Meng Guangcai

00:17:27.559 --> 00:17:29.099
on a construction site.

00:17:29.259 --> 00:17:30.420
Back then at the site,

00:17:31.799 --> 00:17:33.559
Jiao Lijun, Wang Dazhu,

00:17:33.559 --> 00:17:35.920
none of them had any respect
for Huang Mantang,

00:17:36.420 --> 00:17:39.079
thinking him as lazy, gluttonous,
and addicted to gambling.

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:42.420
But out of respect for Meng Guangcai,
no one dared complain anything.

00:17:43.200 --> 00:17:44.380
Then in 1993,

00:17:45.339 --> 00:17:46.599
Meng Guangcai went south,

00:17:47.960 --> 00:17:50.180
and Huang Mantang disappeared.

00:17:50.440 --> 00:17:51.579
1993?

00:17:54.460 --> 00:17:57.720
Master, what's your take
on Huang Mantang's disappearance?

00:17:58.460 --> 00:17:59.519
After 1993,

00:18:00.839 --> 00:18:03.819
I went back to Shaguai Village
to various construction sites,

00:18:03.819 --> 00:18:05.380
and spoke with Principal Chen.

00:18:05.680 --> 00:18:09.579
I learned Huang Mantang had been
hooked on gambling since childhood.

00:18:10.079 --> 00:18:13.519
So it's likely he disappeared
to dodge gambling debts.

00:18:14.519 --> 00:18:18.259
But you just said
Huang Mantang died in 2006?

00:18:19.180 --> 00:18:19.960
Quite sudden.

00:18:21.180 --> 00:18:23.700
I heard he died of cancer
in another place.

00:18:25.799 --> 00:18:27.259
I know what you're thinking.

00:18:28.440 --> 00:18:31.680
When I heard the news,
I was quite surprised too.

00:18:32.180 --> 00:18:33.519
I even went to look into it.

00:18:34.019 --> 00:18:37.920
Huang Mantang is buried
in the local cemetery.

00:18:38.960 --> 00:18:41.220
Master, you know this route well.

00:18:41.759 --> 00:18:44.759
While investigating Huang Mantang's
background, I visited his grave.

00:18:45.460 --> 00:18:46.960
Who buried him here?

00:18:48.059 --> 00:18:49.019
Before I answer you,

00:18:49.019 --> 00:18:52.440
I want to hear
your thoughts on the case.

00:18:53.380 --> 00:18:55.460
Master, we've used up

00:18:55.579 --> 00:18:57.180
half the investigating time
on this case.

00:18:57.460 --> 00:18:59.960
The names Meng Guangcai gave us
are either dead or missing.

00:19:00.380 --> 00:19:01.960
That's way too many coincidences.

00:19:02.599 --> 00:19:03.460
Also, Master,

00:19:03.460 --> 00:19:06.440
so far, we only have
the blood sample as a lead.

00:19:08.019 --> 00:19:12.339
I suspect Meng Guangcai and Wang Dazhu
have been leading us in circles.

00:19:12.460 --> 00:19:14.920
I fear we'd only end up
catching Wang Dazhu,

00:19:15.579 --> 00:19:18.460
and they'll get off the hook
at the lowest cost.

00:19:18.460 --> 00:19:19.140
Exactly.

00:19:19.759 --> 00:19:23.319
Meng Guangcai has made
a seemingly flawless plan.

00:19:24.460 --> 00:19:28.420
Even a gambler like Huang Mantang
has a place to rest in peace. Why?

00:19:28.700 --> 00:19:30.579
The more they try to steer us,

00:19:30.680 --> 00:19:32.680
the less we should follow their lead.

00:19:34.180 --> 00:19:34.839
This way.

00:19:35.920 --> 00:19:39.579
You mean, Huang Mantang's funeral
was also part of their plan?

00:19:40.019 --> 00:19:43.680
Exactly. Huang Mantang's funeral
was handled by Jiao Lijun.

00:19:47.482 --> 00:19:51.962
(Grave of Huang Mantang)

00:19:55.079 --> 00:19:56.920
Who held such a deep grudge against him?

00:20:25.960 --> 00:20:27.819
Stop. Zoom in.

00:20:28.099 --> 00:20:28.599
Yes.

00:20:32.762 --> 00:20:35.079
(Beiyan City Caisheng Group Co., Ltd.)

00:20:35.079 --> 00:20:37.819
Report on any currently active
company projects at any time.

00:20:37.960 --> 00:20:39.960
(Caisheng Group)
Postpone those that haven't started yet.

00:20:40.559 --> 00:20:41.579
You're Jiao Lijun, right?

00:20:42.759 --> 00:20:44.380
I'm Zhang Wei,
Criminal Investigation Unit.

00:20:49.579 --> 00:20:52.259
Zhu Helai's superior?
I've met you before.

00:20:52.519 --> 00:20:55.059
Why didn't you bring Officer Zhu along?

00:20:55.420 --> 00:20:58.099
I need to talk to you.
Let's talk privately.

00:20:58.299 --> 00:20:58.799
No need.

00:20:59.680 --> 00:21:01.220
I do things with integrity.

00:21:01.220 --> 00:21:03.799
These are all my shareholders.
Don't let them misunderstand.

00:21:03.799 --> 00:21:05.420
If you want to talk, let's do it here.

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:06.500
Fine.

00:21:07.839 --> 00:21:10.059
A major criminal case

00:21:10.559 --> 00:21:13.059
requires you to provide details.

00:21:13.680 --> 00:21:15.059
A major criminal case?

00:21:16.759 --> 00:21:18.259
Since this is a major criminal case,

00:21:19.059 --> 00:21:20.579
then let's talk at the police station.

00:21:20.940 --> 00:21:23.700
Once we see Zhu Helai,
we'll settle everything in one go.

00:21:24.090 --> 00:21:28.680
(Beiyan City Caisheng Group Co., Ltd.)

00:21:28.680 --> 00:21:29.680
Mr. Jiao is out.

00:21:30.059 --> 00:21:31.079
- He's out!
- He's out!

00:21:33.960 --> 00:21:34.680
What is this?

00:21:35.000 --> 00:21:35.700
Don't do it.

00:21:36.200 --> 00:21:37.319
- What is this?
- Getting physical?

00:21:37.319 --> 00:21:37.960
Getting physical?

00:21:37.960 --> 00:21:39.519
Cops are hitting people!

00:21:39.519 --> 00:21:40.680
Quiet please.

00:21:40.880 --> 00:21:42.579
This is standard police procedure.

00:21:42.579 --> 00:21:44.200
Please stop filming!

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:44.819
Press freedom.

00:21:44.819 --> 00:21:45.339
Stop filming!

00:21:45.339 --> 00:21:46.960
- Exactly.
- We have press freedom.

00:21:48.180 --> 00:21:48.759
Sir.

00:21:49.380 --> 00:21:52.940
I need to give this to my secretary.
No need for such tension.

00:21:58.700 --> 00:22:01.099
Mr. Jiao, how's the situation
affecting Caisheng Group?

00:22:02.700 --> 00:22:06.000
First, thank you all for your attention
to Caisheng Group.

00:22:06.180 --> 00:22:07.599
We're a private enterprise.

00:22:08.059 --> 00:22:09.420
In the process of development,

00:22:09.680 --> 00:22:14.099
we've created numerous jobs
and substantial tax revenue for Beiyan.

00:22:14.420 --> 00:22:17.059
But regrettably, at this critical time,

00:22:17.099 --> 00:22:19.180
we've had a misunderstanding
with the police.

00:22:19.380 --> 00:22:20.579
As you all know,

00:22:21.819 --> 00:22:24.099
first, our chairman
was detained without cause.

00:22:25.299 --> 00:22:28.680
Then, I was held by police
without justification.

00:22:29.259 --> 00:22:31.460
To clarify,
it's for their investigation.

00:22:33.339 --> 00:22:36.299
Mr. Jiao, will this situation
impact Caisheng Group's IPO?

00:22:36.660 --> 00:22:37.920
I guess

00:22:38.680 --> 00:22:40.599
we must've stepped on someone's toes.

00:22:41.180 --> 00:22:45.380
Someone's abusing power,
using underhanded tactics,

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:47.519
to deliberately suppress Caisheng Group.

00:22:48.299 --> 00:22:51.059
We request your cooperation.
Watch your tone.

00:22:53.319 --> 00:22:54.440
I believe, sure,

00:22:54.559 --> 00:22:58.200
the police will investigate
thoroughly and efficiently,

00:22:58.579 --> 00:23:02.799
restoring clear names
for Beiyan and Caisheng Group.

00:23:03.420 --> 00:23:04.339
Are you done?

00:23:06.319 --> 00:23:07.259
Mr. Jiao, tell us more.

00:23:07.259 --> 00:23:08.680
- Tell us more.
- Thank you all.

00:23:08.680 --> 00:23:11.059
Please support
private enterprises like ours.

00:23:11.059 --> 00:23:11.599
Step back.

00:23:11.599 --> 00:23:12.819
What's the current situation?

00:23:12.819 --> 00:23:13.559
- Exactly.
- Don't go.

00:23:13.559 --> 00:23:14.400
Tell us more.

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:15.500
- Tell us more.
- Don't go!

00:23:15.500 --> 00:23:16.099
Tell us more.

00:23:16.099 --> 00:23:16.759
Move back.

00:23:16.759 --> 00:23:17.299
Mr. Jiao.

00:23:17.599 --> 00:23:18.759
- Mr. Jiao.
- Mr. Jiao.

00:23:18.759 --> 00:23:19.839
Make way please.

00:23:20.940 --> 00:23:21.700
- Tell us more.
- Tell us more.

00:23:21.700 --> 00:23:22.720
Tell us more.

00:23:22.720 --> 00:23:23.440
Tell us more.

00:23:23.880 --> 00:23:26.440
- Mr. Jiao.
- Mr. Jiao.

00:23:26.925 --> 00:23:29.434
(Police)

00:23:31.680 --> 00:23:34.559
You seem quite chummy with the press.

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:35.819
Came prepared?

00:23:37.180 --> 00:23:38.339
You're overthinking.

00:23:39.099 --> 00:23:42.420
The press has freedom
to oversee and report facts.

00:23:43.259 --> 00:23:45.259
I came to cooperate,
which is also a fact, right?

00:23:46.079 --> 00:23:47.220
Do you know Huang Mantang?

00:23:49.079 --> 00:23:49.759
Yes.

00:23:50.579 --> 00:23:51.720
What was your relationship?

00:23:54.500 --> 00:23:55.799
Fellow villagers, you could say.

00:23:55.799 --> 00:23:57.920
We were both from
Shaguai Village, Magou Town.

00:23:58.140 --> 00:24:02.680
After you left Shaguai Village
in 1988, did you stay in touch?

00:24:04.940 --> 00:24:05.799
No.

00:24:06.700 --> 00:24:07.559
Strange.

00:24:07.559 --> 00:24:12.180
My investigation shows he came to Beiyan
and worked construction with you.

00:24:14.799 --> 00:24:19.220
That rang a bell. He did come
but left soon after a few days.

00:24:19.960 --> 00:24:21.180
Why did he seek you out?

00:24:21.460 --> 00:24:24.500
Principal Chen referred him to us.
Since we were from the same village,

00:24:24.579 --> 00:24:28.140
and he couldn't earn decent money,
so he wanted us to help him out.

00:24:29.319 --> 00:24:30.720
Then why did he leave soon?

00:24:31.059 --> 00:24:32.819
Frankly, the man was lazy and shiftless.

00:24:33.559 --> 00:24:35.819
Never a diligent type.

00:24:36.299 --> 00:24:37.920
He won't make money anywhere.

00:24:38.559 --> 00:24:39.380
Then?

00:24:39.559 --> 00:24:42.680
Then, we lost touch.

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:45.299
Where were you this morning?

00:24:45.640 --> 00:24:46.460
In a meeting.

00:24:46.559 --> 00:24:47.420
Where?

00:24:49.819 --> 00:24:51.440
Right where you picked me up.

00:24:52.079 --> 00:24:53.579
All the shareholders witnessed it.

00:24:54.680 --> 00:24:55.500
Sir.

00:24:56.579 --> 00:25:00.700
You brought me in for a major case.

00:25:01.059 --> 00:25:03.059
Was it about Huang Mantang?

00:25:04.460 --> 00:25:05.559
Did you sign this?

00:25:10.170 --> 00:25:12.602
(Cemetery Burial Registration Form)

00:25:16.460 --> 00:25:17.319
I signed it.

00:25:19.319 --> 00:25:20.680
I said you two weren't close.

00:25:21.720 --> 00:25:24.519
But you signed Huang Mantang's
cemetery registration form

00:25:24.519 --> 00:25:26.500
and paid for the burial expenses.

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:29.200
You tell me you two lost contact?

00:25:31.140 --> 00:25:34.579
Look, I admire the Terracotta Army.

00:25:35.640 --> 00:25:38.079
I donated money
to protect national artifacts

00:25:38.380 --> 00:25:39.680
and signed some papers for it.

00:25:39.960 --> 00:25:42.220
Does that mean
I contacted Qin Shi Huang?

00:25:44.200 --> 00:25:45.299
Just kidding.

00:25:46.799 --> 00:25:48.579
Huang Mantang was my fellow villager.

00:25:49.700 --> 00:25:52.839
He died alone and penniless.

00:25:53.079 --> 00:25:56.180
I spent some money to bury him.

00:25:56.180 --> 00:25:57.940
It's not against the law, right?

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:11.920
Zhu, I'm not trying to cause trouble.

00:26:12.380 --> 00:26:15.259
In front of all the shareholders,
your superior

00:26:15.640 --> 00:26:17.640
announced an investigation
into a major case.

00:26:19.220 --> 00:26:22.720
And there's Guangcai.
He's been locked up with no explanation

00:26:22.720 --> 00:26:23.779
or evidence.

00:26:24.140 --> 00:26:26.460
This is damaging the group's reputation,

00:26:26.460 --> 00:26:28.519
so I'm here to understand the situation

00:26:28.799 --> 00:26:30.700
to give the public
and the press some answers.

00:26:30.700 --> 00:26:34.059
Otherwise, legal keeps pushing me
to file a complaint.

00:26:34.059 --> 00:26:35.059
I have to do this.

00:26:36.799 --> 00:26:39.720
Indeed. I know you're busy.
Thanks for coming.

00:26:40.680 --> 00:26:42.380
There's a lot to this situation.

00:26:42.380 --> 00:26:44.920
It's not something easily explained.

00:26:44.920 --> 00:26:45.680
Just one thing.

00:26:46.380 --> 00:26:48.920
For now, don't pursue this.

00:26:49.819 --> 00:26:50.420
Alright.

00:26:52.799 --> 00:26:55.599
Zhu, you know this well.

00:26:56.680 --> 00:26:59.019
To us three, you've
always been a role model.

00:26:59.680 --> 00:27:02.720
Especially Guangcai,
he sees you as his own brother.

00:27:03.299 --> 00:27:06.460
If we make a mistake, you can
scold us or punish us if needed.

00:27:07.339 --> 00:27:10.460
But after that,

00:27:13.519 --> 00:27:15.680
you have to tell us what we did wrong.

00:27:23.460 --> 00:27:25.440
You have rules, so you can't tell.

00:27:25.799 --> 00:27:26.960
Then let me ask differently.

00:27:27.339 --> 00:27:29.099
How long do you plan
to keep us locked up?

00:27:29.839 --> 00:27:31.339
Give me a timeframe.

00:27:34.019 --> 00:27:37.180
Lijun, look, I am here.

00:27:39.579 --> 00:27:41.759
Your questions are fair.

00:27:42.460 --> 00:27:44.460
But I can only tell you one thing.

00:27:45.460 --> 00:27:47.819
We won't wrong him.

00:27:53.079 --> 00:27:55.000
Explain, what happened today?

00:27:55.700 --> 00:27:56.599
It's all my fault.

00:27:57.299 --> 00:27:59.680
I should've anticipated
someone like Jiao Lijun

00:28:00.079 --> 00:28:01.880
would prepare early.

00:28:02.339 --> 00:28:05.680
Now he's using this to pressure us,

00:28:06.960 --> 00:28:09.680
accusing us of violating procedure,
arresting him illegally.

00:28:12.160 --> 00:28:15.160
We just managed
to calm the public opinion,

00:28:16.799 --> 00:28:18.059
yet now it's flared up again.

00:28:18.799 --> 00:28:21.660
Listen, if we can't
produce evidence soon,

00:28:22.299 --> 00:28:24.160
we have to release Meng Guangcai.

00:28:25.180 --> 00:28:26.519
Yes, Chief.

00:28:26.519 --> 00:28:28.880
The priority now
is dealing with Jiao Lijun, right?

00:28:30.819 --> 00:28:33.880
Chief, I brought him in.
It has nothing to do with Master.

00:28:34.039 --> 00:28:36.160
I'll take all the blame myself.

00:28:36.420 --> 00:28:37.940
I'll write a self-criticism first,

00:28:37.940 --> 00:28:39.660
then apologize to Jiao Lijun

00:28:39.819 --> 00:28:42.299
and make a public apology
to Caisheng Group.

00:28:42.420 --> 00:28:44.400
Captain Zhang, am I being unfair to you?

00:28:46.039 --> 00:28:47.180
Get your self-criticism

00:28:47.420 --> 00:28:48.660
on my desk this afternoon.

00:28:49.319 --> 00:28:50.019
Yes.

00:28:52.799 --> 00:28:56.059
I'm off to clean up your mess.

00:29:20.680 --> 00:29:23.900
Master, we finally caught Jiao Lijun.

00:29:23.900 --> 00:29:25.059
Yet now we just let him go?

00:29:28.539 --> 00:29:30.019
Master, not this potato again.

00:29:30.019 --> 00:29:32.180
Eating it every day,
you'll start sprouting potatoes.

00:29:35.099 --> 00:29:35.680
Let's go.

00:29:35.940 --> 00:29:36.660
Where to?

00:29:36.779 --> 00:29:37.940
To see Jiao Lijun again.

00:29:43.059 --> 00:29:44.140
I want to leave.

00:29:45.019 --> 00:29:46.059
But since I'm here,

00:29:46.059 --> 00:29:48.000
returning with nothing won't cut it.

00:29:48.099 --> 00:29:49.940
So I need to file the complaint.

00:29:50.440 --> 00:29:53.140
What's this officer's name and position?

00:29:53.680 --> 00:29:55.920
I need it clear. Don't want
to blame the wrong person.

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:12.799
Zhang Wei.

00:30:18.140 --> 00:30:19.660
We went to the cemetery

00:30:20.039 --> 00:30:21.539
and visited Huang Mantang's grave.

00:30:22.680 --> 00:30:23.920
It brought back a lot

00:30:25.420 --> 00:30:27.720
of memories from
Shaguai Village, Magou Town.

00:30:31.299 --> 00:30:35.720
I remember back then, everyone
looked down on Huang Mantang.

00:30:36.180 --> 00:30:38.140
Especially after the fight
with Zuo Long.

00:30:39.880 --> 00:30:44.019
Back then, only Xue Qin
showed Huang Mantang some kindness.

00:30:45.779 --> 00:30:50.059
Speaking of Xue Qin, she seemed
to care for everyone back then.

00:30:50.559 --> 00:30:51.799
Especially,

00:30:53.160 --> 00:30:54.299
for you.

00:30:59.160 --> 00:31:00.599
What are you trying to say?

00:31:01.539 --> 00:31:05.819
I just remember back
in the video theater in Magou Town,

00:31:06.304 --> 00:31:07.488
(her notebook was there.)

00:31:09.140 --> 00:31:12.539
(Jiao Lijun)
(And your name was written all over it.)

00:31:13.299 --> 00:31:15.019
That couldn't be any coincidence.

00:31:17.180 --> 00:31:19.059
Mr. Jiao, you're such a charming man,

00:31:19.660 --> 00:31:21.019
but you've never married.

00:31:23.019 --> 00:31:24.539
Are you waiting for someone?

00:31:28.634 --> 00:31:35.226
(Beiyan Police Station)

00:31:35.559 --> 00:31:36.380
Zhu,

00:31:36.920 --> 00:31:39.299
hope you can be fully prepared

00:31:39.299 --> 00:31:40.799
before coming to me.

00:31:41.680 --> 00:31:42.500
Jiao Lijun.

00:31:45.039 --> 00:31:46.039
When necessary,

00:31:47.720 --> 00:31:50.319
I will call you and Xue Qin
to come at any time.

00:31:51.720 --> 00:31:52.779
Be prepared.

00:31:55.839 --> 00:31:56.640
Any time.

00:32:04.539 --> 00:32:05.720
At this moment,

00:32:06.039 --> 00:32:07.420
we need to stay sharp.

00:32:07.640 --> 00:32:08.799
Don't get discouraged.

00:32:09.720 --> 00:32:10.660
Don't worry, Master.

00:32:11.059 --> 00:32:13.420
Master, you've been
investigating this case for years.

00:32:13.559 --> 00:32:15.759
What do you think about
Xue Qin's brother, Xue Yonghui?

00:32:20.500 --> 00:32:21.220
Captain Li.

00:32:21.640 --> 00:32:23.559
Perfect timing. I wanted to ask

00:32:24.420 --> 00:32:29.640
if the welfare factory owned by
Xue Yonghui is part of Caisheng Group.

00:32:30.900 --> 00:32:34.000
Yes, it's a subsidiary
under Caisheng Group,

00:32:34.099 --> 00:32:35.819
- but unrelated to the man in black.
- Why?

00:32:38.799 --> 00:32:40.920
The factory hires disabled workers,

00:32:41.400 --> 00:32:44.220
and even Xue Yonghui himself
is disabled. What do you think?

00:32:47.180 --> 00:32:48.059
Turn? How?

00:32:50.039 --> 00:32:50.680
Lijun.

00:32:51.880 --> 00:32:52.539
Turn!

00:32:57.559 --> 00:32:58.099
Lijun.

00:32:58.440 --> 00:32:58.940
Lijun.

00:33:00.299 --> 00:33:01.180
Lijun, wait.

00:33:01.799 --> 00:33:02.400
Lijun.

00:33:02.400 --> 00:33:07.808
(Personal Rankings)

00:33:18.299 --> 00:33:19.220
Long time no see.

00:33:22.202 --> 00:33:25.568
(Office)

00:33:29.279 --> 00:33:33.660
I didn't expect your welfare factory
to be doing so well now.

00:33:36.599 --> 00:33:39.519
Yonghui, it's been so long
since we last met.

00:33:40.779 --> 00:33:42.839
Aren't you going to show me
around the factory?

00:33:57.099 --> 00:33:59.180
This place is quite far
from the city center.

00:33:59.880 --> 00:34:01.779
Is it convenient
for the workers to commute?

00:34:02.779 --> 00:34:03.660
We have dorms.

00:34:04.039 --> 00:34:05.920
Then let's go check out
some other places.

00:34:10.639 --> 00:34:11.900
Why did you run around?

00:34:12.300 --> 00:34:13.920
Do you know you almost got us killed?

00:34:14.440 --> 00:34:16.000
(Chai Daqing, Xue Yonghui's driver)
No, Lijun.

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:17.280
I-I didn't go anywhere.

00:34:17.280 --> 00:34:18.380
- No?
- Lijun.

00:34:20.679 --> 00:34:21.300
Lijun.

00:34:22.360 --> 00:34:23.136
Lijun.

00:34:24.440 --> 00:34:27.280
Think anyone in this world
still remembers you?

00:34:27.639 --> 00:34:29.159
Will anyone burn incense for you?

00:34:30.900 --> 00:34:32.280
- Speak!
- Lijun.

00:34:32.320 --> 00:34:33.900
- Speak!
- Lijun.

00:34:40.840 --> 00:34:42.860
Are you trying to kill me now?

00:34:43.639 --> 00:34:45.320
At worst, we'll die together.

00:34:45.719 --> 00:34:48.039
I didn't expect your welfare factory
to be this large.

00:34:48.679 --> 00:34:51.360
You should be the star enterprise
of Caisheng Group, right?

00:34:52.340 --> 00:34:54.579
You don't deserve to live in this world.

00:34:55.579 --> 00:34:58.019
You should've died long ago!

00:34:58.519 --> 00:35:01.139
You should've died long ago!

00:35:01.340 --> 00:35:02.280
Mr. Xue.

00:35:07.519 --> 00:35:08.400
What is this place?

00:35:08.599 --> 00:35:10.119
The dorm area and my office.

00:35:11.000 --> 00:35:12.099
Take me for a look around.

00:35:27.619 --> 00:35:28.840
This is your office, right?

00:35:30.139 --> 00:35:31.320
Looks nice.

00:35:32.860 --> 00:35:34.780
I bet you're not here
just for a visit today.

00:35:36.599 --> 00:35:38.219
Principal Chen once said

00:35:38.860 --> 00:35:42.760
among the kids taking the exams,
you were the most promising.

00:35:43.880 --> 00:35:45.599
If it weren't for that injured arm,

00:35:46.360 --> 00:35:48.380
you would've achieved
even greater things.

00:35:49.780 --> 00:35:54.219
You injured that arm in 1993, right?

00:35:55.400 --> 00:35:56.579
Hit by a car.

00:36:00.940 --> 00:36:01.820
By a minivan?

00:36:02.780 --> 00:36:04.619
It was so long ago. I hardly remember.

00:36:08.039 --> 00:36:13.019
Your sister and brother-in-law
were really worried back then,

00:36:13.840 --> 00:36:15.519
feeling like the world had collapsed.

00:36:16.320 --> 00:36:17.820
At that time, they ran around,

00:36:18.219 --> 00:36:20.099
trying to find a good path for you.

00:36:23.940 --> 00:36:25.320
Officer Zhu, I'm very busy today.

00:36:25.320 --> 00:36:27.139
If there's nothing urgent,

00:36:27.599 --> 00:36:28.599
let's talk another day.

00:36:41.780 --> 00:36:42.880
I'll ask you about someone.

00:36:44.079 --> 00:36:47.360
When was the last time
you saw Huang Mantang?

00:36:49.559 --> 00:36:51.940
Your sister used
to take good care of him.

00:36:52.539 --> 00:36:53.519
I don't recall.

00:37:54.860 --> 00:37:55.880
Remember this.

00:38:18.639 --> 00:38:19.619
(When necessary,)

00:38:19.860 --> 00:38:22.440
I will call you and Xue Qin
to come at any time.

00:38:23.119 --> 00:38:24.099
(Be prepared.)

00:39:04.099 --> 00:39:05.019
Had too much to drink?

00:39:09.360 --> 00:39:10.599
Go lie down over there.

00:39:11.599 --> 00:39:12.900
Looks like you had quite a few.

00:39:15.360 --> 00:39:18.500
Qin, can I say something?

00:39:19.940 --> 00:39:20.679
Go ahead.

00:39:25.519 --> 00:39:26.659
What is it?

00:39:26.659 --> 00:39:27.559
Fine, I'm leaving.

00:39:42.940 --> 00:39:45.159
It's been six years. That incident

00:39:46.519 --> 00:39:48.639
has been weighing on me like a rock.

00:39:49.860 --> 00:39:50.719
I can't shift it

00:39:51.659 --> 00:39:52.579
or move it.

00:39:54.579 --> 00:39:56.099
And I have to face you

00:39:57.500 --> 00:39:58.579
and Guangcai every day.

00:39:59.679 --> 00:40:00.719
Especially Xiaoliang.

00:40:02.260 --> 00:40:05.179
Seeing him is like a torture to me.

00:40:05.179 --> 00:40:07.260
It's like a constant reminder.

00:40:11.599 --> 00:40:14.360
I can't pretend that nothing happened.

00:40:16.360 --> 00:40:18.559
Qin, I regret it.

00:40:21.420 --> 00:40:24.820
If I had taken you away
from Shaguai Village back then...

00:40:25.380 --> 00:40:26.599
If that night...

00:40:30.059 --> 00:40:31.940
I want to push that rock away.

00:40:31.940 --> 00:40:34.300
I don't know what I can do
to make up for it.

00:40:34.300 --> 00:40:35.320
Alright, stop talking.

00:40:36.119 --> 00:40:39.619
Sorry, I-I drank too much.

00:40:40.840 --> 00:40:42.400
Let bygones be bygones.

00:40:42.539 --> 00:40:43.872
What matters now

00:40:44.992 --> 00:40:47.800
is to live well and look ahead.

00:41:46.780 --> 00:41:48.940
Master, you mentioned Xue Qin last time.

00:41:49.179 --> 00:41:50.420
Should we tell Chief Liu?

00:41:50.420 --> 00:41:51.820
That was for Jiao Lijun's ears.

00:41:51.820 --> 00:41:53.599
If we question Xue Qin,
I wouldn't tell him.

00:41:53.760 --> 00:41:54.820
I can't let them prepare.

00:41:55.619 --> 00:41:56.860
So, what do we do next?

00:41:56.860 --> 00:41:57.820
Monitor Jiao Lijun.

00:41:57.820 --> 00:41:59.119
His next moves are crucial.

00:41:59.820 --> 00:42:01.952
Interrogate Meng Guangcai
and tell him something new.

00:42:02.860 --> 00:42:03.880
(Fifth Interrogation)
Long time no see.

00:42:07.820 --> 00:42:08.719
That long?

00:42:09.360 --> 00:42:10.920
We keep dragging this out.

00:42:12.920 --> 00:42:16.019
You suffer, and I don't enjoy it either.

00:42:16.280 --> 00:42:18.059
Let's wrap this case up.

00:42:18.519 --> 00:42:19.840
So, we can have peace of mind.

00:42:20.179 --> 00:42:21.360
That would be best.

00:42:21.360 --> 00:42:23.099
But you came to see me,

00:42:23.780 --> 00:42:25.659
probably because
you've hit a wall recently.

00:42:27.820 --> 00:42:28.619
Guangcai.

00:42:29.659 --> 00:42:31.000
Since the day you came in here,

00:42:31.000 --> 00:42:33.420
your Caisheng Group
hasn't sat idle for a single day.

00:42:33.420 --> 00:42:34.760
Someone's riling up the press,

00:42:34.760 --> 00:42:36.860
creating public pressure against us.

00:42:36.860 --> 00:42:38.579
This is a coordinated effort,

00:42:38.579 --> 00:42:40.059
and it's working pretty well.

00:42:41.860 --> 00:42:45.639
You won't rest until you've
destroyed our company?

00:42:49.159 --> 00:42:53.039
Tell me. Which one in our group
are you suspecting now?

00:42:53.840 --> 00:42:54.760
You know him well.

00:42:55.139 --> 00:42:58.019
Meng Xiaoliang's biological father,

00:43:02.039 --> 00:43:02.920
Jiao Lijun.

00:43:15.599 --> 00:43:16.820
Officer Zhu was right.

00:43:16.820 --> 00:43:18.619
Jiao Lijun did come looking for Xue Qin.

00:43:23.900 --> 00:43:25.519
Zhu Helai went to the welfare factory.

00:43:26.900 --> 00:43:28.079
Things are getting worse.

00:43:28.340 --> 00:43:30.639
He's dead set on bringing Guangcai down.

00:43:31.219 --> 00:43:32.579
And he subtly

00:43:34.119 --> 00:43:35.000
mentioned you.

00:43:36.639 --> 00:43:39.360
Qin, I'll do everything I can
to help Guangcai.

00:43:40.000 --> 00:43:41.300
Getting Guangcai out

00:43:41.860 --> 00:43:44.159
is safer for Xiaoliang, for you,

00:43:45.000 --> 00:43:47.659
and for us.

00:43:49.639 --> 00:43:50.719
What do you want to do?

00:43:58.300 --> 00:44:03.039
I've said it.
The biggest regret of my life

00:44:04.360 --> 00:44:05.860
was not taking you away back then.

00:44:10.400 --> 00:44:13.679
Well, I'm always indecisive.

00:44:16.360 --> 00:44:18.059
But I can't be so anymore.

00:44:26.920 --> 00:44:30.500
I mean, if I end up in there too,

00:44:31.920 --> 00:44:33.599
you have to handle
everything for a while.

00:44:34.840 --> 00:44:36.159
Take good care of yourself.

00:44:39.840 --> 00:44:41.900
Don't worry. Guangcai will get out.

00:44:53.019 --> 00:44:54.300
You're not surprised at all.

00:44:55.619 --> 00:44:57.260
Seems you knew about this all along.

00:44:58.059 --> 00:45:00.599
No wonder. Jiao Lijun is so clever,

00:45:00.599 --> 00:45:04.159
yet you handed the group's main business
over to Wang Dazhu.

00:45:04.360 --> 00:45:05.619
It's because of Xue Qin.

00:45:06.599 --> 00:45:09.659
Everything makes sense now.

00:45:09.880 --> 00:45:11.400
It's all because of Xue Qin.

00:45:13.760 --> 00:45:15.639
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

00:45:17.559 --> 00:45:19.619
For someone as proud as you,

00:45:19.619 --> 00:45:21.360
there can only be one reason

00:45:21.360 --> 00:45:22.599
to accept all this calmly.

00:45:22.860 --> 00:45:24.260
You care about Meng Xiaoliang,

00:45:24.260 --> 00:45:26.659
and Jiao Lijun
is Meng Xiaoliang's biological father.

00:45:26.659 --> 00:45:29.599
In a way, you're protecting Jiao Lijun.

00:45:33.860 --> 00:45:36.360
Officer Zhu, if you have evidence,

00:45:37.159 --> 00:45:38.619
then arrest Jiao Lijun.

00:45:40.300 --> 00:45:41.900
I'd like to see how far you cops

00:45:42.360 --> 00:45:44.880
are going to push our group.

00:45:46.360 --> 00:45:50.000
Let's see how much blame
Liu Hua can take for you.

00:45:51.019 --> 00:45:52.360
But I'm warning you.

00:45:52.360 --> 00:45:55.380
If you make
these baseless accusations public,

00:45:59.360 --> 00:46:00.420
I won't let you off.

00:46:54.820 --> 00:46:56.360
Big boss is really different.

00:46:56.360 --> 00:46:58.760
The group's in such bad shape,
yet he strolls in the park?

00:46:59.300 --> 00:47:01.139
And he took a detour to come here.

00:47:02.000 --> 00:47:03.179
Probably meeting someone.

00:47:04.059 --> 00:47:06.059
Captain Li, look. Someone we know.

00:47:07.159 --> 00:47:08.860
Why here? Couldn't we talk at home?

00:47:09.280 --> 00:47:10.119
No.

00:47:10.500 --> 00:47:11.380
Jiao Lijun.

00:47:12.320 --> 00:47:13.880
My dad's been arrested.

00:47:14.059 --> 00:47:15.619
What exactly are you scheming?

00:47:20.320 --> 00:47:21.019
Xiaoliang.

00:47:22.380 --> 00:47:24.119
Don't you understand me and your dad?

00:47:24.119 --> 00:47:25.500
We're trying to solve this.

00:47:26.159 --> 00:47:27.860
Cut the act, Jiao Lijun.

00:47:28.420 --> 00:47:29.760
I saw it.

00:47:30.360 --> 00:47:32.300
You've long wanted
to break up our family.

00:47:32.860 --> 00:47:38.099
Seems Meng Xiaoliang
has zero trust in his 'uncle' either.

00:47:38.420 --> 00:47:39.659
My mom is a big fool

00:47:40.119 --> 00:47:41.659
to trust someone like you.

00:47:41.659 --> 00:47:43.519
You're thrilled my dad got arrested.

00:47:43.519 --> 00:47:45.159
You've always wanted to be with my mom.

00:47:46.440 --> 00:47:49.500
I'm warning you, stay away from my mom.

00:47:50.099 --> 00:47:51.019
Heard me?

00:47:55.519 --> 00:47:59.000
You're this big,
yet that's all you've got?

00:48:12.400 --> 00:48:13.019
Use this.

00:48:13.119 --> 00:48:14.000
You're a man.

00:48:15.059 --> 00:48:17.940
Once you decide something,
do it till the end.

00:48:18.599 --> 00:48:20.099
Don't be indecisive.

00:48:20.559 --> 00:48:21.119
Take it

00:48:26.059 --> 00:48:27.059
and hit me here.

00:48:34.300 --> 00:48:35.179
Come on!

00:48:48.320 --> 00:48:49.820
Xiaoliang, remember this.

00:48:50.800 --> 00:48:52.159
Violence won't solve anything.

00:48:53.800 --> 00:48:56.659
But I hope you remember this anger
and courage you're feeling now.

00:48:58.159 --> 00:48:59.260
From now on,

00:48:59.539 --> 00:49:02.059
I want you to use that courage
to protect your mom.

00:49:03.420 --> 00:49:05.920
Because in this world,
only your mom loves you the most.

00:49:07.360 --> 00:49:09.059
She can do anything for you.

00:49:10.559 --> 00:49:12.119
Don't misunderstand her like that.

00:49:21.260 --> 00:49:22.300
You're grown up now.

00:49:23.519 --> 00:49:24.900
Protect your mom.

00:49:28.599 --> 00:49:29.559
Go home.

00:49:35.800 --> 00:49:37.260
So, we can confirm the relationship

00:49:37.260 --> 00:49:39.599
between Jiao Lijun
and Meng Xiaoliang now.

00:49:40.019 --> 00:49:42.519
And Jiao Lijun keeps
meeting with Xue Qin.

00:49:43.099 --> 00:49:45.059
Let's issue an order, detain him first.

00:49:45.300 --> 00:49:47.019
If he runs, it'll be a real mess.

00:49:47.380 --> 00:49:49.539
Haven't you learned
from Meng Guangcai's incident?

00:49:50.099 --> 00:49:52.860
You should first prove who
Meng Xiaoliang's biological father is,

00:49:52.860 --> 00:49:53.920
then make the arrest.

00:49:53.920 --> 00:49:56.780
You can't arrest someone first
and then figure that out.

00:49:56.780 --> 00:49:57.440
Go by the...

00:49:57.440 --> 00:49:58.380
If we delay,

00:49:58.380 --> 00:50:00.440
what if he runs away
right under our noses?

00:50:00.440 --> 00:50:01.099
Chief!

00:50:02.860 --> 00:50:03.519
What is it?

00:50:04.380 --> 00:50:05.519
Jiao Lijun is back.

00:50:43.161 --> 00:50:48.185
=The Silent Rift=